{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_03_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 二人きりのショッピング",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.033333333333333326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "買い物に付き合ってくれって意味だったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what you meant was that you wanted me to go shopping with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.1260999362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……すみません、すみません……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ I’m so sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1260999362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.0587529182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに真剣な顔で言うからびっくりしたよ\n俺はてっきり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really threw me for a loop with your serious expression.\nI almost thought…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8378103528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、もう忘れて下さい\n恥ずかしいですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ don’t say anymore‚ {user}…\nI’m so embarrassed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや、俺も早合点してすまなかった\nまさか、天動さんが俺にそんなこと言うはずないしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ well‚ I’m at fault too for jumping to conclusions.\nI should have known better than to think you’d say something like that to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　そ、それは必ずしもないとは\n言い切れないんじゃありませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Well‚ eh‚\nthat’s not necessarily true…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　あくまで一般論ですが！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m just talking in general terms!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーとアイドルだってお互い\n惹かれ合えば、そうなっても――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I mean‚ it’s not out of the question\nthat an idol and manager could be attracted to each other—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、ないよ\n少なくとも俺はそんなよこしまな目で君達を見てない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope‚ no way.\nI don’t think about that stuff when interacting with you guys.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、どんな目で見てるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you think about‚ then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、まずマネージャーとして見てる\nあとは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m thinking from the perspective of a manager‚ for starters.\nAnd then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "妹みたいな感じかな？\n奥山さんが末っ子で、天動さんは長女みたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… thinking like a brother with his sisters‚ I guess?\nOkuyama is like the little sister‚ and you’re like the big sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3089115332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "…………妹\nそうですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sister.\nI see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0822449238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　天動さん、急に難しい顔してどうかした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is something wrong‚ Tendo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、なんでもありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ no‚ it’s nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと……誘っておいて\n置いて行かないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ wait up! Don’t just leave me behind like that…\nYou were the one who asked me to come…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 766.6666667000044,
          "startTime": 77.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、優にはあそこのバッグがいいかも\nでも、すみれとお揃いにした方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I think Yu would like that bag.\nBut maybe I should match it with Sumire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ、天動さん\n俺、今更ながら思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Say‚ Tendo…\nMaybe it’s a little late to bring this up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さんと奥山さんへのクリスマスプレゼントを\n選びたいっていうなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re picking Christmas presents\nfor Suzumura and Okuyama‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8768713107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "俺より女の子を誘った方が良かったんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "wouldn’t it have been better to come with another girl?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It has?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "だってそうだろ？\n寮には他のグループの子達が沢山いるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You could have asked someone\nfrom one of the other groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3775744348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
