      "text": "そ、そうか……でも全然自信ないな……\n女の子にあげて喜ばれるプレゼントなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… I’m not sure if I’ll be of any help though…\nI have no idea what kind of gifts a girl would like…",
